Job Description
1. Desired individual must play a leading role in e-marketing of company's product and services.2. He/She should understand the organizational needs and must be capable of utilizing the best possible channels for business to business online marketing.3. Under the guidance of Head of Business Development, selected individual must create and organize the annual marketing plan, and he/she must possess the capability to execute it accordingly.
Job Specification
KomKonsult (Pvt) Ltd is looking for a Marketing expert of B2B, having 2 years of experience at least, preferably with know how of Telecom/IT sector. Excellent communication and written skills along with experience of any CRM tool are prerequisites
